  "text": "Theorem 2 (Quantum Minimum Finding [CITATION_1] ). Let a 1 , . . . , a n be integers, accessed by a procedure P. There exists a quantum algorithm that finds min n i=1 {a i } with success probability at least 2/3 using O( √ n) applications of P.",
